{"tid":1649361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞活動嘅手足唔該入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-12T15:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T17:02:07.000Z","uid":127479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"872b92751dfcc59208c7109bb01ef4f1d6722276","tid":1649361,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"From tg<br />\n<br />\n大家都攰。<br />\n但點解我哋對被性侵嘅手足、極速被火化嘅手足可以完全冇反應？<br />\n個晚大家話訓唔著，好沉重，咁跟住呢？<br />\n第一個女義士失去右眼，大家仲識叫狗還眼；<br />\n而家有人被雞姦、被自殺，我哋點解可以放軟晒手腳？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">搞活動嘅手足，你哋plan活動前會唔會諗製造多一個可以籌到好多人嘅活動？<br />\n有行動有目的嘅行動，唔係單單搞打飛機大會呢類對政權不痛不癢嘅嘉年華就當做咗嘢。<br />\n個政權做盡壞事，每星期都升級，<br />\n相反我哋一星期比一星期退步。</span><br />\n<br />\n下一個公眾假期已經要去到十二月，<br />\n唔通你以為兩個月後大家真真正正頹晒之後仲可以吹到雞？"},{"pid":"7cf29380ae4684f65bcc4eedcc6b43d5f0bf20bf","tid":1649361,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/3DeFV2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2F3DeFV2.jpeg&h=11fde298&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0df82f66934dbc1ccb705bcb17e41fe8eb29ac8","tid":1649361,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Go5RhcJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGo5RhcJ.jpg&h=eb92e4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pweeZq5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpweeZq5.jpg&h=6de7c02d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb7bf24375371257e63fedc14ca2216183da4723","tid":1649361,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TE4OjrN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTE4OjrN.jpg&h=bda39d81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/strXXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstrXXdt.jpg&h=30a79e20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f5543d8161a209e02357d846e009af8cdb48eae","tid":1649361,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fc9e0a75033bc7fd42b8d161f79d3dcf76565b05","tid":1649361,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"除咗摺紙唱歌<br />\n可唔可以貼返多啲連儂牆<br />\n煲大新屋嶺、緊急法、警暴、罷買<br />\n我哋一停，一怠惰，就好難有返Momentum <br />\n唔係為咗做俾侵侵睇，係為咗我哋要贏<br />\n<br />\n仲有，我唔知大家係覺得無用定點<br />\n帶個口罩有幾大難？<br />\n文宣手足不如放啲獨立包裝口罩喺牆度，或者朝早喺巴士站/派口罩<br />\n政權見我哋個個都龜縮，佢就會愈來愈放肆"},{"pid":"c622e0b1d374878c041e63f6586249be7a412129","tid":1649361,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6115mJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6115mJH.jpg&h=9f29cd44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8UKCg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8UKCg3.jpg&h=5b817178&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2425eb7f1874af72839a6c2d5ab2aaf769e2e629","tid":1649361,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qO2sz3T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqO2sz3T.jpg&h=004a2a66&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYhHoXf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYhHoXf.jpg&h=5ece176c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"934bc60d6185b0fd4b02